Crazy this time last year I invited all of my friends up to my birthday… I guess it was more of a goodbye celebration 😅 
Because my friends got together and could tell I needed help, I took the pills to far, the lifestyle to far. The party was over. 
So I checked myself into a hospital and found an amazing team of doctors and therapists to help me. 
I’m a year sober (off pills) and a year older 
Can’t Believe I’m 27…. 
I love you guys so much thank you for changing my life forever. 
I’m so ready for the future and taking life a lil slower haha
